The treasurer of Eldoret's 20 Minibus Sacco was abducted by unknown people on Tuesday.Judy Nyambura's family said she did not return after the people called her from her house.Margaret Mumbi said the abductors sent a message saying they had taken the 30-year-old woman and that they would not see her again."We were told her mobile phone signal was last traced to Kitale but it has gone off," she said. "We do not know of any differences she had with anyone and are pleading with police to do everything possible to trace her."Nyambura has worked with the sacco, the largest in Eldoret, for more than two years.The incident was reported at Langas police station.Read: Bus driver and tout deny abducting traffic officer